These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, kale, garlic, watermelon
City: new-york, marseilles, miami, edinburgh
House: modern, art-deco, gothic-revival, farmhouse
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person traveling to miami is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the modern house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the gothic-revival house is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person eating kale is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Food   | kale    | watermelon    | lettuce      | garlic    |
| City   | edinburgh | marseilles | miami | new-york |
| House     | farmhouse  | modern       | art-deco    | gothic-revival     |

