.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
City: hamburg, prague, san-francisco, berlin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
House: craftsman, farmhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, dahlia, poppy
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
3. the gothic-revival house is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the cape-cod house and the person who growsiris##2
6. the person who growspoppy is between the person watching western movies and the gothic-revival house##2
7. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City         | berlin | prague    | san-francisco  | hamburg    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| House           | gothic-revival      | cape-cod       | farmhouse      | craftsman       |
| Flower         | bellflower    | poppy | dahlia | iris |

