.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend, pall-mall, aristoff
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, action, satire, horror
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, rose, azalea
1. the person watching satire movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar        | blend | pall-mall     | ritmeester   | aristoff     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Movie-Genre         | sports   | satire | horror       | action    |
| Flower   | rose    | marigold | amaryllis  | azalea    |

