.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, marigold, rose
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, reading, fishing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | iris  | rose | zinnia     | marigold |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea  | coffee | lemonade       |
| Hobby           | reading       | camping    | fishing      | video-games           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

