The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, australian, german, malaysian
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 2. the polish is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the german##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the malaysian and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | card-games         | cooking         | magic-tricks     | filmmaking      |
