.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, watermelon, banana, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, apricot, mauve, ebony
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, baking, reading, woodworking
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person eating watermelon is between the fan of folk and the person who likes ebony##2
3. the person who likes mauve is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who likes apricot##2
4. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes mauve is the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food           | banana | watermelon | avocado  | raspberry |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Color   | ebony   | apricot      | mauve   | grey   |
| Hobby         | reading   | woodworking    | magic-tricks | baking   |

