The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, writer, librarian, firefighter
4 different games are played: snooker, go, mah-jongg, poker
 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is the librarian##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the librarian and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person playing poker##1
 5. the firefighter is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person playing go##1
 7. the doctor is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the librarian is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | light-blue | ivory | red  | pink  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Job   | doctor   | librarian   | firefighter | writer |
| Game     | snooker    | poker   | go    | mah-jongg  |

