3. the doctor is on the left of the social-worker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person who growsaconite##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the paramedic##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | balloon-flower   | aconite | tulip |
